comments.text:
This is next-level stuff, Ben—seriously impressive. It’s like watching the digital equivalent of cloning your best sales rep, teaching it to speak five languages (or at least five channels), and then giving it infinite coffee so it never stops working.

What really stands out here is how practical this implementation is. A lot of folks talk about AI in sales like it’s some futuristic concept, but you’ve shown how it’s already being used today to reduce overhead, increase speed to lead, and (crucially) not fry your team’s brain managing a dozen DMs across three platforms. The before/after snapshot—5 people manually qualifying leads vs. one smart AI setup freeing up 80% of that team—is the kind of ROI most agencies dream of.

I can instantly duplicate our posts across multiple profiles without juggling between platforms, freeing up tons of time. Just last week, I duplicated an Instagram post across 8 platforms in seconds.
